
Streamlit App – Business Requirements (Refined)
Overall Idea
Replace the current Excel-based effort tracker with a simple, structured internal app that:

Makes it easy for team members to update progress
Gives leads a clear, real-time view of work and effort
Allows basic management of team members
Removes Excel pain points (manual formatting, overwrites, inconsistencies)


Core Tabs in the Application
Tab 1: Task Updates (Primary Working Screen)
This is the main screen used by the team daily.
Purpose
Allow team members to create, update, and maintain tasks as work progresses.
