Business Rules

Only active team members can be assigned to tasks
Names should be consistent (no free‑text typing per task)
Helps avoid Excel problems like duplicate or inconsistent names


General Business Expectations
Usability

App should feel simpler than Excel
Minimal clicks to update daily progress
Clear and readable layout

Consistency

Structured fields instead of long free‑text
Common statuses and naming
Easier historical tracking

Transparency

Everyone sees the same data
Progress and effort are visible and current
History of updates is preserved


Success Criteria
The app is successful when:

Team members prefer it over Excel
Updates happen continuously, not in bursts
Leads rely on the app for visibility
Excel is no longer needed for effort tracking
